headline: State Street Announces Partnership with Harris | Oakmark for State Street Alpha®
summary: BOSTON, December 10, 2024--State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT) announced today that Harris | Oakmark has gone live with State Street Alpha®, the firm’s front-to-back asset servicing platform for institutional investment managers, following the selection of State Street to be their strategic operating partner less than a year ago. Harris | Oakmark, a Chicago-based investment management firm with approximately $104 billion of assets under management as of September 30, 2024, serves as the adviser
